{"tid":2028093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人民日報：以國安法應對攬炒風險","createTime":"2020-05-21T15:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T19:39:09.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ce31ad646033246ed0bf66b8224e6cfce59405","tid":2028093,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"人民日報：中央建全香港國安法是權力和責任所在<br />\n21.05.2020 23:42<br />\n<br />\n官方人民日報發表評論文章，形容人大會議將審議通過《建立健全香港特區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制的決定》，是維護國家安全的重要舉措，亦是維護&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;的根本之策，文章指，國家安全立法屬於中央事權，在香港特區國家安全受到現實威脅和嚴重損害、特別行政區政府根本無法自行完成立法的情況下，中央主動從國家層面進行有關立法，正是為了補上國家安全存在的漏洞，把面臨脫軌危險的&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;拉回正軌及繫上安全帶。中央主動填補法律漏洞，為&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;修堤築壩，這既是不得已而為，也是權力和責任所在。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，香港已經成為國家安全的一個突出風險點。這個風險，來自&ldquo;港獨&rdquo;組織和本土激進分離勢力的活動日益猖獗，來自反對派毫無底線的社會攬炒、經濟攬炒、政治攬炒，來自暴力恐怖活動的不斷升級，來自外部勢力赤裸裸地干涉香港事務，來自&ldquo;台獨&rdquo;&ldquo;港獨&rdquo;勢力的勾結合作，無不嚴重挑戰&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;原則底線，無不對國家主權安全造成嚴重危害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289192&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289192%26csid%3D261_341&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=bc2b3dc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289192&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"5657f39d9c60f6f5783171f9573c3ec0efcee090","tid":2028093,"uid":209097,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"只要香港變左焦土 就唔會俾人攬炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05104ff90438694d29ffdec00fbb5dc3567c12e8","tid":2028093,"uid":210608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"原來小數派咁驚攬炒"},{"pid":"af32f1e9e9e440e41829f887e756e5471b8acd20","tid":2028093,"uid":285551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"呢個世界根本無台獨呢樣嘢，點同個唔存在嘅勢力勾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5463d2962c27a67a83045c030e3742b0b23624fe","tid":2028093,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"以國安法完成攬炒成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0e22cce60bedc51da5a2201ec3dc6889c1f6cf","tid":2028093,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:53:10.000Z","msg":"佢係用國安法成功攬炒喎"},{"pid":"5a9a1f273d82fd077fe39f71ed0e6580da916b3a","tid":2028093,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"為左唔比攬炒，我先將佢變成焦土睇你炒到咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda6e7aa43e4ab70dfe74f3417ecaea982d9767d","tid":2028093,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:54:31.000Z","msg":"國安法就係攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝人民日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9efcc4a37dac2db71fab5d63c9d4bd4f8183bf","tid":2028093,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:54:42.000Z","msg":"2011年到2020年樓價負擔指數由11升到21<br />\n即係人工被大減一半<br />\n其實經濟點攬炒對打工仔都完全無影響"},{"pid":"3f2460df5cbfddb51a09eb122c4e77a7481bf275","tid":2028093,"uid":122940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:54:53.000Z","msg":"係加速攬炒喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca582245c7a2eae3df46354f9b7202bb4a77a33","tid":2028093,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"我地抗爭要成功 首要改變返我地套mindset<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024244</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"23a8a007226d044abff306b31a2f727ba99081ea","tid":2028093,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB